                    <p>Artificial Intelligence is revolutionizing the educational landscape by:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Personalizing learning experiences for students</li>
                        <li>Automating routine tasks for educators</li>
                        <li>Providing intelligent tutoring systems</li>
                        <li>Enhancing accessibility and inclusion</li>
